trans-unit.source: Defines how to format the text inside of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Define como formatar o texto dentro de um <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used by <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.CutCopyMaskFormat%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TextMaskFormat%2A> to control how text is returned—in the first case, by performing a cut and copy operation, and in the second place, by using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Text%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Essa enumeração é usada por <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.CutCopyMaskFormat%2A>e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TextMaskFormat%2A>para controlar como o texto é retornado — no primeiro caso, executando uma operação recortar e copiar e em segundo lugar, usando o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Text%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Text%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TextMaskFormat%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.CutCopyMaskFormat%2A>

trans-unit.source: Return only text input by the user.
trans-unit.target: Retorne apenas a entrada de texto pelo usuário.

trans-unit.source: Return text input by the user as well as any literal characters defined in the mask.
trans-unit.target: Retorne entrada de texto, o usuário, bem como caracteres literais definidos na máscara.

trans-unit.source: Return text input by the user as well as any instances of the prompt character.
trans-unit.target: Retorne a entrada de texto, o usuário, bem como todas as instâncias de caractere de prompt.

trans-unit.source: Return text input by the user as well as any literal characters defined in the mask and any instances of the prompt character.
trans-unit.target: Retorne a entrada de texto, o usuário, bem como qualquer caractere literal definido na máscara de e todas as instâncias de caractere de prompt.
